content: anirudhmakhana: Made a significant contribution by creating and merging the gelato plugin relay (PR #2799), a substantial addition with +47,356 lines added and 4,685 lines removed across 421 files. This major development effort, which took 16 hours to merge, primarily consisted of code (56%) and configuration files (28%). Activity was concentrated on a single day this month, resulting in a focused but isolated contribution period.
